  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Development of forecasting models to assess the potential impact of tax reforms in Vietnam</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To strengthen the capacity of the Ministry of Finance (MoF) to better define tax policy and develop appropriate CIT and VAT legislation consistent with its socio-economic development goals. This is to be done by enhancing the capacity of the National Institute for Finance to develop appropriate forecasting models to assess the potential impacts of changes in taxation legislation and effectively communicate the results to senior policy makers.</narrative>
  </description>
